* 2019: [[Mary_Jane_Irwin|Mary Jane Irwin]], [[Pennsylvania_State_University|Pennsylvania State University]], for her extensive contributions to EDA and the community.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.semi.org/en/communities/esda/mediaLibrary/20191107_PhilKaufmanAward/|title=2019 Phil Kaufman Award – ESD Alliance|website=esd-alliance.org|language=en-US|access-date=2020-09-11}}</ref>
